   <text:p text:style-name="Standard"><text:span text:style-name="T13">â</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T13">Non, lui rÃ©pondit-on. Nous sommes Ã©trangers au pays.</text:span></text:p>
