   <text:p text:style-name="Standard"><text:span text:style-name="T13">â</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T13">OhÂ ! câest donc vous qui lâavez priseÂ ? demandai-je.</text:span></text:p>
